d one medal, courtesy of the bronze secured by the Blitzboks  There could be more to add on Monday, with hopes high that South Africa could secure their first gold medal through swimming sensation Tatjana Smith.\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 658, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 365, \"end\": 379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 428, \"end\": 430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1108437705729441e-20, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 568, \"end\": 580, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.999999935093458, \"rank\": 6.34209878731245e-08, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pieter Coetze is also a realistic medal contender in the pool later on Monday.\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 738, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"BADMINTON  Women's Singles, Group H (2.50pm):Johanita Scoltz vs Jin Wei Goh (Malaysia)  CYCLING  Men's MTB cross-country (2.10pm):Alan Hatherley  HOCKEY  Women's Pool B (5.30pm):Team SA vs Argentina  RUGBY SEVENS  Women's Pool B (2pm):Team SA vs Great Britain  SKATEBOARDING  Men's street prelims (12noon):Brandon Valjalo  SURFING  Men's round 3 (7pm):Jordy Smith vs Alonso Per Correa (Peru)  SWIMMING  Men's 100m backstroke, final (9.19pm):Pieter Coetze  Women's 100m breaststroke, final (9.25pm):Tatjana Smith  Tatjana Smith, formerly Schoenmaker,won her heat and semi-finalin the 100m at the Paris La Defense Arena on Sunday, touching the wall in both races on the day in 1min 05.00sec.\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 1429, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 804, \"end\": 807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"score\": 0.8307159473209844, \"rank\": 0.20377459854289404, \"text\": \"Jin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\"}, {\"begin\": 808, \"end\": 811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cao_Wei\", \"score\": 0.9990273069792673, \"rank\": 0.0007233242823741034, \"text\": \"Wei\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cao_Wei\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cao_Wei\"}, {\"begin\": 817, \"end\": 825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\", \"score\": 0.9614682003667779, \"rank\": 0.04007597483823539, \"text\": \"Malaysia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\"}, {\"begin\": 923, \"end\": 925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1108437705729441e-20, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 929, \"end\": 938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9979589730726283, \"rank\": 0.002044588505317054, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 986, \"end\": 999, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.6790413179755428, \"rank\": 0.4562140719896712, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1126, \"end\": 1130, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peru\", \"score\": 0.9999216349481427, \"rank\": 7.836347555272065e-05, \"text\": \"Peru\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peru\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peru\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am just so grateful swimming to be good times again,\\\" the Team SA superstar said.\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1515, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1497, \"end\": 1499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1108437705729441e-20, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have not been close to my time from Tokyo (1:04.82), so to be swimming my best times since then is an amazing feeling.\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1555, \"end\": 1560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9983727060001157, \"rank\": 0.0016283931670140349, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am just happy to be enjoying every race and it does not matter what times I do put up.\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1726, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's about the experience and how happy I am to be here doing what I am doing.\\\"\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1806, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Coetze is still only 20, but joined the medals conversation for the men's 100m backstroke.\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1898, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was lightning quick in evening, breaking the African record with a 52.63 touch, for tie second and tied third overall heading into Monday night's final.\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 2054, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Since 1992, South Africa has won 82 golds, 56 silvers and 54 bronzes.\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2125, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2068, \"end\": 2080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.999999935093458, \"rank\": 6.34209878731245e-08, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"WIN R2 000: Take The South African's SASSA Survey  The South African is hiring!\", \"from\": 2127, \"to\": 2206, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2127, \"end\": 2130, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"score\": 0.9999977076316908, \"rank\": 2.2785120591586096e-06, \"text\": \"WIN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\"}, {\"begin\": 2131, \"end\": 2133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"score\": 0.999444867311232, \"rank\": 0.0002916961691495577, \"text\": \"R2\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Freelance writing positions available  Follow The South African on Facebook for the latest local and international news  Follow The South African's WhatsApp channel for the latest sport, lifestyle and local news  Follow The South African on X for the latest, breaking news  A brand new shopping mall is coming to Pretoria East, bringing major retailers and new convenience to the area.\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2592, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2355, \"end\": 2363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 0.9999988830715536, \"rank\": 1.1169296098115228e-06, \"text\": \"WhatsApp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/res